    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there, neighbor! I\u2019m honestly a bit heartbroken to be listing my pride and joy, but it\u2019s time for this absolute gem to find a new home where she\u2019ll be just as cherished. If you\u2019re like me and appreciate a car that\u2019s been truly pampered, you\u2019re going to fall in love. She\u2019s been tucked away in a climate-controlled garage and hand-waxed more times than I can count\u2014honestly, she looks and feels like she just rolled off the showroom floor. It\u2019s so rare to find one kept in this kind of breathtaking shape these days. No stress, no surprises, just pure driving joy waiting for you. Come on over, let\u2019s grab a coffee, and I\u2019ll show you why this is the one you\u2019ve been waiting for!",
